2008-05-08 Damien Douxchamps http://damien.douxchamps.net/
	* SVN 557: Update the lt verions to 23,0,1. RELEASE 2.0.2
	           (Note: the SOversion is 22.0.2)
	* SVN 556: the wrong file was uploaded for the new example, fixed.
	
